com.alicecallsbob.fcsdk.android.aed

Interface Topic

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ListenerTarget<TopicListener>

    public interface Topic
extends ListenerTarget<TopicListener>
    A representation of a single Topic within AED. This object allows the publishing and accessing of data within the topic.
